{"tid":1177547,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"響呢度呼籲各位居港外國藉巴絲寫信比你地國家駐港領使館，表達對逃犯條例既擔憂","createTime":"2019-05-29T22:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T06:11:26.000Z","uid":120678,"like":94,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"416e52533a66df7071bb8d10d7cd14a29d944ba0","tid":1177547,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:18:39.000Z","msg":"無論你地係美國藉、加拿大藉、澳洲藉、紐西蘭藉、BC、葡藉，或者其他罕見國家既國藉<br />\n請你地抽出十幾分鐘既時間，寫一封簡短既信件比你地國家駐港領使館，表達對逃犯條例既關注、擔憂同不滿<br />\n小弟係現居於港既加藉人士，而家響度寫緊一封email比加拿大駐港總領使館就呢條條例表達關注<br />\n希望各位有外國藉既巴絲都做類似既事<br />\n雖然個人力量微不足道，但如果人多做既話，有機會可以逼到我地各自祖國既領使同政府表態<br />\n例如，居港加拿大人已經有30幾萬，當中只要有幾千人寫信去領使館，係有機會引起到加國政府注意<br />\n希望各位外國藉巴絲善用大家既西方國家護照，行使你享用領使服務既權利，一齊幫幫香港度過呢一關<br />\n多謝各位"},{"pid":"eaaac1743a307f54b18eb485f5f1d1ab3ed81c57","tid":1177547,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6823ec3238721ec5b007d72d97979ffd474ef869","tid":1177547,"uid":196924,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T23:16:04.000Z","msg":"其實個<span style=\"color: red;\">籍</span>字係咪咁難認<br />\n十個post有七個錯"},{"pid":"e941a5110cd123bc43b187e45604f8d63411bc82","tid":1177547,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T00:39:03.000Z","msg":"係.但你用中文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74acfdb35666aa8c5b524959ef68449e0720bc87","tid":1177547,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6823ec3238721ec5b007d72d97979ffd474ef869","tid":1177547,"uid":196924,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,